metadata.name: Antennae Galaxies
metadata.description:
Artist Vincent Zuniaga
Title: Antennae Galaxies
Digital Bodypainting
Resolution: 6120px x 4079px 300 dpi
Format  PNG

Antennae Galaxies are a beautiful artwork done by the Universe and one of my favorites. For this very reason was my genesis painting for this project.

I create artwork combining my photography and digital painting. I called it “Digital Bodypainting Project” 
I do a photo session with a model with the project in mind, to get the “canvas” I will need for the digital bodypainting.
Sometimes just working with just the shape of the body and others working with the texture of the skin.

Galaxies, Nature, Landscape and seascape are the themes I prefer.
 
Thank you
Vincent
